data.description: The Irving is a single-story, 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom bathroom home plus a study. This home features approximately 2,608 square feet of living space. The beautiful kitchen includes modern finishes, stainless steel appliances, and a gas range. The extra-large pantry gives additional storage in the open-concept kitchen. Enjoy preparing meals and spending time together gathered around the kitchen island with a double sink. The spacious Bedroom 1 suite is located off the family room and includes a large walk-in closet and a relaxing spa-like walk-in shower. Also, off the family room is an extra office space with a closet inside, which gives some flexibility to the space. Next to the kitchen is bedroom 2, which would make a perfect guest suite with its own full bathroom next to it. Youll enjoy added security in your new D.R. Horton home with our Home is Connected features. With D.R. Horton's simple buying process and ten-year limited warranty, there's no reason to wait! (Prices, plans, dimensions, specifications, features, incentives, and availability are subject to change without notice obligation)
